Package: PlusMinusData
Title: Downloads play-by-play data from espn.com and performs interactive record linkage
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Francesca", "Matano", email = "fmatano@andrew.cmu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows data driven sports enthusiasts to easily download play-by-play data
              from ESPN. The functions within this package help getting the data to compute
              Plus Minus estimates in soccer
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Imports: rvest,
    xml2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/fmatano/PlusMinusData

